 1, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Geopolitics", "Iran"]}}, {"id": "2075049804510433550", "url": "https://x.com/aeberman12/status/2075049804510433550", "text": "Drill, baby, drill needs price, baby, price @amberdawn1786 \n\nTrump wants more U.S. oil production while undermining the prices required to justify it\n\nThat is not an energy strategy\n\nIt's political theater colliding with geology & capital discipline\n\n#Oil #Energy #OOTT #DrillBabyDrill #OilPrices #Sh", "time": "02:50", "author": "aeberman12", "author_name": "Art Berman", "followers": 53616, "views": 2973, "likes": 26, "replies": 1, "retweets": 5, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bearish", "emotional_sentiment": "Negative", "topics": ["Shale/US production", "Prices/technicals"]}}, {"id": "2075058945941536832", "url": "https://x.com/aeberman12/status/2075058945941536832", "text": "WTI price has undershot its attractor & is now $15 less than the implied marginal price\n\nThis is normal discovery behavior as markets reassess geopolitical developments\n\nFundamentals are secondary to the changing probability landscape\n#energy #OOTT #oilandgas #WTI #CrudeOil #fintwit #OPEC #Commoditi", "time": "03:26", "author": "aeberman12", "author_name": "Art Berman", "followers": 53616, "views": 3545, "likes": 30, "replies": 6, "retweets": 3, "quotes": 2, "bookmarks": 2, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Prices/technicals", "Geopolitics"]}}, {"id": "2075064127324659922", "url": "https://x.com/Amalteya3000/status/2075064127324659922", "text": "It will be incredibly strange if Brent oil doesn't return to growth and go above 80 now.\n\nGuys, do you really expect SoH to fully opening in 2026? Do you really expect a real and stable peace/nuke deal between Trump and Iran? \n#oott #Hormuz", "time": "03:46", "au